* 500-stage CMOS inverter chain (no subcircuits) using BSIM4 models

* Models
.model nmos nmos (level=14 version=4.8.2)
.model pmos pmos (level=14 version=4.8.2)

* Simulation flags
.options acct
*.options num_threads=32
.sparse
.output Results/inv500.raw

VDD vdd 0 1.0
VIN n0 0 PULSE(0 1.0 0 10p 10p 2n 4n)
Cload n500 0 1f

* Inverters expanded inline: Mp=PMOS pull-up, Mn=NMOS pull-down
Mp1 n1 n0 vdd vdd pmos W=1u L=45n
Mn1 n1 n0 0 0 nmos W=0.5u L=45n
Mp2 n2 n1 vdd vdd pmos W=1u L=45n
Mn2 n2 n1 0 0 nmos W=0.5u L=45n
